pageContext.claim: “No matter how much I accomplish during the ridiculous standard of the first 100 days, & it has been a lot (including S.C.), media will kill!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump calls the 100-day mark a ridiculous standard but before the election he grandly announced a 100-day he titled the "Contract with the American Voter." Few of the promises made in that documents have been kept in Trump's first 100 days.
